  lib/main.dart (created)
</span><span class="c">  ...
</span><span class="go">  ios/Runner.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/contents.xcworkspacedata (created)
  .metadata (created)
  hello_app.iml (created)
Running "flutter pub get" in hello_app...                           4.0s
